<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>
<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="義解" xml:id="gsz0743b04shiZhiXuan"><lb
ed="T" n="0743b04"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0743b04"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000035014"><placeName>彭州</placeName><placeName>丹景山</placeName></placeName><persName key="A000753">知玄</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0743b05"/><persName key="A000753">釋知玄</persName><ptr target="#n963"/>，字<persName key="A000753">後覺</persName>，姓<name>陳</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000036649"><placeName>眉州</placeName><placeName>洪雅</placeName></placeName>人也。曾祖<lb
ed="T" n="0743b06"/><persName key="A009696">圖南</persName>，任<placeName key="PL000000035878"><placeName>梓州</placeName><placeName>射洪縣</placeName></placeName>令。祖<persName key="A009698">憲</persName>，考<persName key="A000216">邈</persName>，皆名場不<lb
ed="T" n="0743b07"/>捷。母<persName key="A022276">魏<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>夢月入于懷，因而載誕，雖乳哺<lb
ed="T" n="0743b08"/>未能言，見佛像僧形，必含喜色。<date key="j20187332019097" from-iso="+0815-01-01" to-iso="+0815-12-31">五歲</date>，<ref target="#A009698" type="person">祖</ref>令<lb
ed="T" n="0743b09"/>詠花，不數步成云：「花開滿樹紅，花落萬枝<lb
ed="T" n="0743b10"/>空，唯餘一朵在，明日定隨風。」<ref target="#A009698" type="person">祖</ref>吟歎不懌<lb
ed="T" n="0743b11"/>曰：「<ref target="#A009698" type="person">吾</ref>育此<ref type="person" target="#A000753">孫</ref>，望其登甲科，雪二代之恥。今<lb
ed="T" n="0743b12"/>見<ref type="person" target="#A000753">孺子</ref>志矣，非貽厥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g473"/>也已，必從空門，乖<lb
ed="T" n="0743b13"/>始望也。」<date key="j20194642019828" from-iso="+0817-01-01" to-iso="+0817-12-31">七歲</date>，果遇<persName key="A009699">法泰<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>在<placeName key="PL000000036644">寧夷寺</placeName>講<lb
ed="T" n="0743b14"/>《涅槃經》。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000036644">寺</ref>與居隣，<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>日就講集所，一聆法<lb
ed="T" n="0743b15"/>語，若覩前因。是夕夢其寺殿，<persName key="A002799">佛</persName>手摩其頂。<lb
ed="T" n="0743b16"/>寤啟<ref target="#A009698" type="person">祖父</ref>，乞為勤策<ptr type="glossary" target="#g964"/>，親黨觀其必不可抑<lb
ed="T" n="0743b17"/>奪，故聽之。<date key="j20209252021289" from-iso="+0821-01-01" to-iso="+0821-12-31">年十一</date>，遂其削髮。乃隨<ref type="person" target="#A009699">師</ref>詣<placeName key="PL000000034973">唐<lb
ed="T" n="0743b18"/>興邑四安寺</placeName>，授大經四十二卷<ptr target="#n3327"/>，<persName key="A002000">遠<roleName>公</roleName></persName>《義疏》<ptr target="#n965"/>、<persName key="A008877">辯<lb
ed="T" n="0743b19"/>空師</persName>《圓旨》，共一百二十五萬言。皆囊括深奧<lb
ed="T" n="0743b20"/>矣。方<date key="j20216552022019" from-iso="+0823-01-01" to-iso="+0823-12-31">年十三</date>，指擿緇徒，露老成<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g672"/>之氣。時丞<lb
ed="T" n="0743b21"/>相<persName key="A009701">杜<roleName>公</roleName>元頴</persName>作鎮<placeName key="PL000000035107">西蜀</placeName>，聞<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>名，命升<anchor xml:id="beg0743001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>堂</sic><corr>座</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0743001"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0743b22"/>講談于<placeName key="PL000000034706"><placeName>大慈寺</placeName><placeName>普賢閣</placeName></placeName>下。黑白眾日計萬許<lb
ed="T" n="0743b23"/>人，注聽傾心，駭歎無已。自此<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>人弗厈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g822"/>其<lb
ed="T" n="0743b24"/>名，號<persName key="A000753">陳菩薩</persName>耳。傳云：「<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>前身名<persName key="A001385">知鉉</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000035338"><placeName>漢州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0743b25"/><placeName>三學山</placeName></placeName>講《十地經》，感地變瑠璃焉。<ptr target="#n335"/>」<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>於<placeName key="PL000000034714">淨<lb
ed="T" n="0743b26"/>眾寺</placeName><persName key="A009703">辯貞<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>所受具戒，纔聽「毘尼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>」，續通<lb
ed="T" n="0743b27"/>《俱舍》<ptr target="#n1429"/>，則<placeName key="PL000000034660">長十山</placeName><persName key="A009704">固<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>之付授焉。復從<ref type="person" target="#A009699">本師</ref><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g190"/><lb
ed="T" n="0743b28"/>下<placeName key="PL000000000078">三峽</placeName>，歷<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄</placeName>，抵于<placeName key="PL000000042260"><placeName>神京</placeName><placeName>資聖寺</placeName></placeName>。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042260">此寺</ref>四<lb
ed="T" n="0743b29"/>海三學<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g182"/>之人會要<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1198"/>之地，<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>敷演經論，僧俗仰<pb ed="T" n="0743c" xml:id="T50.2061.0743c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0743c01"/>觀，戶外之屨日其多矣。<persName key="A004169">文宗皇帝</persName>聞之，宣入<lb
ed="T" n="0743c02"/>顧問，甚愜皇情。後學《唯識論》於<placeName key="PL000000042134">安國</placeName><persName key="A009706">信<roleName>法<lb
ed="T" n="0743c03"/>師</roleName></persName>。又研習外典<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g32"/>，經籍百家之言，無不該綜<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g350"/>。<lb
ed="T" n="0743c04"/><persName key="A000753">玄</persName>每恨鄉音不堪講貫<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g1247"/>，乃於<placeName key="PL000000036615">象耳山</placeName>誦《大<lb
ed="T" n="0743c05"/>悲呪》，夢神僧截舌換之。明日，俄變<name>秦</name>語矣。<lb
ed="T" n="0743c06"/>有<persName key="A009709">楊茂孝</persName>者，鴻儒也，就<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>尋究內典，直欲<lb
ed="T" n="0743c07"/>效<persName key="A001869">謝康樂</persName>注《涅槃經》，多執卷質疑，隨為剖<lb
ed="T" n="0743c08"/>判。致書云：「方今海內龍象，非<ref type="person" target="#A000753">師</ref>而誰？」次<persName key="A009710">揚<lb
ed="T" n="0743c09"/><roleName>刑部</roleName>汝士</persName>、<persName key="A009711">高<roleName>左丞</roleName>元裕</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042182">長安</placeName><persName key="A009713"><anchor xml:id="beg0743sgsz2"/>揚<anchor xml:id="end0743sgsz2"/>魯士</persName>咸造門<lb
ed="T" n="0743c10"/>擬結蓮社<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n966"/>。甞一日<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>宴坐，見<persName key="A009709">茂孝</persName>披紫服、<lb
ed="T" n="0743c11"/>戴碧冠，三<anchor xml:id="beg0743sgsz3"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0743sgsz3"/>畢，乘空而去。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>令人偵問，<persName key="A009709">茂<lb
ed="T" n="0743c12"/>孝</persName>其夕誡其子曰：「<ref target="#A009709" type="person">吾</ref>常欲落髮披緇，汲瓶<lb
ed="T" n="0743c13"/>挈屨，侍<persName key="A000753">玄<roleName>公</roleName></persName>，所累者簪冕也。<ref target="#A009709" type="person">吾</ref>蓋棺時，殮<lb
ed="T" n="0743c14"/>以紫袈裟，碧芙蓉冠。」至是方驗先見矣。<persName key="A006570">武<lb
ed="T" n="0743c15"/>宗</persName>御宇，初尚欽<name>釋</name>氏，後納蠱惑者議，望祀<lb
ed="T" n="0743c16"/><placeName key="PL000000055457">蓬萊山</placeName>，築高臺以<anchor xml:id="beg0743002"/>祈<anchor xml:id="end0743002"/>羽化。雖諫官抗疏，<lb
ed="T" n="0743c17"/>宰臣屢言，終不迴<ref target="#A006570" type="person">上</ref>意。因<date when-iso="+0843-07-15" key="j20291552029155">德陽節</date><ptr target="#n967"/>，緇、黃會<lb
ed="T" n="0743c18"/><placeName key="PL000000042361">麟德殿</placeName><ptr target="#n968"/>，獨詔<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>與道門敵言，神仙為可學<lb
ed="T" n="0743c19"/>不可學耶？<ref target="#A006570" type="person">帝</ref><anchor xml:id="beg0743003"/>叉<anchor xml:id="end0743003"/><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g39"/>手付<persName key="A002104">老</persName>氏中「理大國若<lb
ed="T" n="0743c20"/>烹小鮮<ptr target="#n969"/>」義，共黃冠往復。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>陳帝王理道，教<lb
ed="T" n="0743c21"/>化根本，言神仙之術，乃山林間匹夫獨擅高<lb
ed="T" n="0743c22"/>尚之事業，而又必資宿因，非王者所宜。辭<lb
ed="T" n="0743c23"/>河下傾，辯海橫注，凡數千言。聞者為之股慄，<lb
ed="T" n="0743c24"/>大忤<ref target="#A006570" type="person">上</ref>旨，左右莫不色沮。左護軍<persName key="A004339">仇士良</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0743c25"/>內樞密<persName key="A000908">楊欽義</persName>惜<ref type="person" target="#A000753">其</ref>才辯，恐將有厈<ptr type="glossary" target="#g822"/>逐之<lb
ed="T" n="0743c26"/>命，乃密諷貢《祝堯詩》。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>立成五篇，末章云：<lb
ed="T" n="0743c27"/>「生天本自生天業，未必求仙便得仙。鶴背<lb
ed="T" n="0743c28"/>傾危龍背滑，君王且住一千年。」<ref target="#A006570" type="person">帝</ref>覽詩微解。<lb
ed="T" n="0743c29"/><ref target="#A006570" type="person">帝</ref>雖不納忠諫，而嘉其識見口給也。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>即<pb ed="T" n="0744a" xml:id="T50.2061.0744a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0744a01"/>歸<placeName key="PL000000034776">巴岷</placeName>舊山，例施巾櫛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g970"/>，而存戒檢愈更甄<lb
ed="T" n="0744a02"/>明。<anchor xml:id="beg0744001"/>方<anchor xml:id="end0744001"/>扁舟入<placeName key="PL000000028612">湖</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000028611">湘</placeName>間，時<persName key="A009714">楊<roleName>給事</roleName>漢公</persName>廉問<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g979"/><lb
ed="T" n="0744a03"/><placeName key="PL000000032245">桂嶺</placeName>，延止<placeName key="PL000000032260">開元佛寺</placeName>。屬<persName key="A003667">宣宗</persName>龍飛，<persName key="A009714">楊<roleName>公</roleName></persName>自<lb
ed="T" n="0744a04"/>內樞統左禁軍，以冊定功高，請復興<placeName key="PL000000048207">天竺</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0744a05"/>教，奏乞訪<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>聲迹。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>復挂壞衣<ptr type="glossary" target="#g971"/>，歸<placeName key="PL000000042226">上國寶<lb
ed="T" n="0744a06"/>應寺</placeName>。屬壽昌節<ptr target="#n980"/>講讚，賜紫袈裟，署為三教<lb
ed="T" n="0744a07"/>首座。<ref target="#A003667" type="person">帝</ref>以舊藩邸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g785"/>造<placeName key="PL000000042176">法乾寺</placeName>，詔<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>居寺之<lb
ed="T" n="0744a08"/><placeName key="PL000000042177">玉虛亭</placeName>。<date key="j20313512031351" when-iso="+0849-07-19"><name>大中</name>三年誕節</date>，詔諫議<persName key="A009721">李貽孫</persName>、給事<lb
ed="T" n="0744a09"/><persName key="A009714">楊漢公</persName>，緇黃鼎列論義，大悅<persName key="A003667">帝</persName>情。因奏天<lb
ed="T" n="0744a10"/>下廢寺基各勅重建，大興<name>梵</name>剎，<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>有力焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0744a11"/>命畫工圖形于禁中，其優重如是。與相國<lb
ed="T" n="0744a12"/><persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>公</roleName>休</persName>友善，同激揚中興教法事。<date from-iso="+0854-02-05" key="j20330132033367" to-iso="+0855-01-25">八年</date>，上<lb
ed="T" n="0744a13"/>章乞歸故山，大行利濟，受益者多。<date from-iso="+0881-02-07" key="j20428772043063" to-iso="+0881-08-12"><name>廣明</name>二<lb
ed="T" n="0744a14"/>年</date>春<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n982"/>，<persName key="A005228">僖宗</persName>違難<placeName key="PL000000035107">西蜀</placeName><ptr target="#n981"/>，後遣<persName key="A009724">郭遵泰</persName>齎璽書，<lb
ed="T" n="0744a15"/>肩輿詔赴行在。<ref type="person" target="#A005228">帝</ref>接談論，頗解上心。左軍<lb
ed="T" n="0744a16"/>容<persName key="A000230">田令孜</persName>與諸達官，問道勤重<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g250"/>。<persName key="A005228">帝</persName>欲旌其<lb
ed="T" n="0744a17"/>美，令諸學士撰<persName key="A000753">玄<roleName>師</roleName></persName>號，皆未愜旨。乃揮御<lb
ed="T" n="0744a18"/>翰云：「<ref type="person" target="#A005228">朕</ref>以開示悟入《法華》之宗旨也。悟者，<lb
ed="T" n="0744a19"/>覺也，明也，悟達大道，悟佛知見。」又云：「悟者<lb
ed="T" n="0744a20"/>一剎那，不悟河沙劫，所以悟者真乘了然成<lb
ed="T" n="0744a21"/>佛之義。今賜『<persName key="A000753">悟達國師</persName>』為號。雖曰強名，用<lb
ed="T" n="0744a22"/>表<ref type="person" target="#A005228">朕</ref>意。」<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>陳讓不遂，乃乞歸<placeName key="PL000000035032">九隴</placeName>舊廬。於<lb
ed="T" n="0744a23"/><date key="j20436352043635" when-iso="+0883-03-07">正月二十一日</date>臥內<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n985"/>，見所曾遊歷聖境名跡，<lb
ed="T" n="0744a24"/>皆見在前。<date key="j20436512043651" when-iso="+0883-03-23">二月七日</date>，聞空聲曰：「必生淨土。」<lb
ed="T" n="0744a25"/>乃訊之云：「孰之語耶？」空又譍曰：「佛也。」<date notBefore-iso="+0883-08-11" key="j20437922043820" notAfter-iso="+0883-09-08">七月<lb
ed="T" n="0744a26"/>中</date>，聞戶外有格鬪之聲，逡巡<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g608"/>一菩薩降于<lb
ed="T" n="0744a27"/>庭前，事摩滅<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g986"/>矣，漸迫僅<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>身，丁寧讚喻：「勿<lb
ed="T" n="0744a28"/>以此苦為累也。」言訖而沒。又於一夕，有一<lb
ed="T" n="0744a29"/>珠自<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>左足下流去，苦楚萬端，諦視其珠<pb ed="T" n="0744b" xml:id="T50.2061.0744b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0744b01"/>中明明有「<persName key="A000909">晁錯</persName>」二字。乃知<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>是<persName key="A009725">袁盎</persName>也，曾<lb
ed="T" n="0744b02"/>因七國反，<persName key="A009725">盎</persName>奏斬<persName key="A000909">錯</persName>，以謝<persName key="A000910">吳</persName>、<persName key="A000911">楚</persName>諸王，故為<lb
ed="T" n="0744b03"/>嬰撓耳。召弟子<persName key="A001365">慈燈</persName>附口上遺表，囑令棄<lb
ed="T" n="0744b04"/>屍，半飼魚腹，半啗鳥獸。<ref type="person" target="#A000753">吾</ref>久與西方淨土<lb
ed="T" n="0744b05"/>有期如斯。諈諉<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g987"/>訖，右脇面西而逝，享年七<lb
ed="T" n="0744b06"/>十三，僧臘五十四。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName><date notBefore-iso="+0860-12-21" key="j20355242040636" notAfter-iso="+0874-12-20"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0744sgsz1"/>咸<anchor xml:id="end0744sgsz1"/>通</name>中</date>曾遊<placeName key="PL000000004372">澤州</placeName>，追<lb
ed="T" n="0744b07"/>問<persName key="A002000">小遠<name>法師</name></persName>，同年亦同終日月焉<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n988"/>。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>堅守<lb
ed="T" n="0744b08"/>禁戒，少欲，過中不食蔬果，服唯布褐，臥則<lb
ed="T" n="0744b09"/>蒭秆<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g989"/>。而六時行道，夜臥一更，餘則禪坐。等視<lb
ed="T" n="0744b10"/>眾生，無貴賤少長，待之如一。素結情好深<lb
ed="T" n="0744b11"/>者<persName key="A003624">裴<roleName>相國</roleName>休</persName>。初，<persName key="A003624">裴</persName>鎮<placeName key="PL000000027429">荊門</placeName>，<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>遊<placeName key="PL000000005250">五臺山</placeName>，路<lb
ed="T" n="0744b12"/>出<placeName key="PL000000027770">渚宮</placeName>，贈遺初無所取。<persName key="A003624">裴</persName>知其儉約，密<lb
ed="T" n="0744b13"/>遣人沿路以供之，若<persName key="A002599">蘇秦</persName>遣舍人陰資奉<lb
ed="T" n="0744b14"/><persName key="A009391">張儀</persName>也<ptr target="#n1024"/>。甞經<placeName key="PL000000043916"><placeName>駱谷</placeName><placeName>真符縣</placeName></placeName><persName key="A022313">雍<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>家枕潭，潭<lb
ed="T" n="0744b15"/>中有大魚，如龍四足，而齒牙纖利，其家日<lb
ed="T" n="0744b16"/>飼以食，已四世矣。或欲網釣之意，則輒雲<lb
ed="T" n="0744b17"/>霧晦冥焉。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>扣船撫其頂，瞪目而鼓躍，即<lb
ed="T" n="0744b18"/>為受歸依。未幾，乃寄夢<persName key="A022313">雍<roleName>氏</roleName></persName>曰：「我謝<ref type="person" target="#A022313">汝</ref>累<lb
ed="T" n="0744b19"/>世護念，今受歸依，已生天而永訣矣。」次為<lb
ed="T" n="0744b20"/><placeName key="PL000000034983"><placeName>導江</placeName><placeName>玉壘山</placeName></placeName>神<persName key="A022314">李氷</persName>廟、<placeName key="PL000000035662">益昌</placeName>北郭龍門神，偕<lb
ed="T" n="0744b21"/>受戒法，罷其血食歟。有<persName key="A009732">李商隱</persName>者，一代文<lb
ed="T" n="0744b22"/>宗，時無倫輩，常從事<placeName key="PL000000005199">河東</placeName><persName key="A009810">柳<roleName>公</roleName></persName><placeName key="PL000000035550">梓潼</placeName>幕，久<lb
ed="T" n="0744b23"/>慕<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>之道學，後以弟子禮事<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>，時居<placeName key="PL000000042210">永崇<lb
ed="T" n="0744b24"/>里</placeName>，<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>居<placeName key="PL000000042218">興善寺</placeName>。<persName key="A009732">義山</persName>苦眼疾，慮嬰<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g990"/>昏瞽，遙<lb
ed="T" n="0744b25"/>望禪宮，冥禱乞願。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>明旦寄《天眼偈》三章，<lb
ed="T" n="0744b26"/>讀終疾愈。迨乎<persName key="A009732">義山</persName>臥病，語僧錄<persName key="A009802">僧徹</persName>曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0744b27"/>「<ref type="person" target="#A009732">某</ref>志願削染為<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>弟子，臨終寄書偈決別。」<lb
ed="T" n="0744b28"/>云。<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>生常著《如來藏經會釋疏》二卷，命<persName key="A009802">僧<lb
ed="T" n="0744b29"/>徹</persName>撰《法鑑》以照像，若《十翼》<ptr target="#n991"/>焉。《大無量壽經<pb ed="T" n="0744c" xml:id="T50.2061.0744c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0744c01"/>疏》二卷。<persName key="A009802">僧徹</persName>著《法燈》，類章指焉。《勝鬘經疏》<lb
ed="T" n="0744c02"/>四卷，<persName key="A009802">僧徹</persName>著《法苑》以錯綜，猶緯書<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n992"/>焉。又《般<lb
ed="T" n="0744c03"/>若心經》、《金剛經》各有《疏義》。此外<placeName key="PL000000042002">秦</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀</placeName>之間，作<lb
ed="T" n="0744c04"/>釋氏雜文、外篇<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n993"/>、箴論、碑誌、歌詩，錄成二十餘<lb
ed="T" n="0744c05"/>卷，<anchor xml:id="beg0744sgsz2"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0744sgsz2"/>懺文六卷，通計三十萬言。後遷塔于<placeName key="PL000000035020"><placeName>茶<lb
ed="T" n="0744c06"/>籠山</placeName><placeName>附聖寺</placeName></placeName>矣。<date from-iso="+0882-01-27" key="j20432312043614" to-iso="+0883-02-14"><name>中和</name>二年</date>，弟子左街僧錄<persName key="A009802"><persName>淨<lb
ed="T" n="0744c07"/>光大師</persName><persName>僧徹</persName></persName>述傳，法孫右街僧錄<persName key="A009803">覺輝</persName>，<persName key="A009803">輝</persName>弟<lb
ed="T" n="0744c08"/>子<placeName key="PL000000000117">偽蜀</placeName><persName key="A001381">祐聖國師</persName>重孫<persName key="A001381">光業</persName>僧錄<ptr target="#n1020"/>，綿綿瓜瓞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1022"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0744c09"/>皆名公也。<placeName key="PL000000042848">鳳翔府</placeName>寫<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>真，<persName key="A009732">李義山</persName>執拂<anchor xml:id="beg0744sgsz3"/>侍<anchor xml:id="end0744sgsz3"/>立<lb
ed="T" n="0744c10"/>焉。</p><p><lb
ed="T" n="0744c11"/>系曰：「<persName key="A000753">玄<roleName>公</roleName></persName>何云<persName key="A009725">袁盎</persName>，又為<persName key="A001385">知鉉</persName>二人後身<lb
ed="T" n="0744c12"/>耶？」通曰：「人壽百年，自<date from-iso="+0025-02-15" key="j17302372052494" to-iso="+0907-06-09"><name>漢</name>至<name>唐</name></date>，<persName key="A000753">玄</persName>幾經出沒<lb
ed="T" n="0744c13"/>乎骸山淚海<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1023"/>，斷可知矣。然則<persName key="A000753">玄<roleName>公</roleName></persName>多才行道，<lb
ed="T" n="0744c14"/>近古罕聞，法嗣蕃昌，他莫與議也。」</p>
